<p>An activist briefly replaced Iran’s current national flag with a pre-1979, shah-era banner at the Iranian embassy in London on Saturday, as crowds gathered nearby to demonstrate. Video shared on social media showed the person scaling to a balcony and unfurling the older emblem while demonstrators cheered below. UK police arrested two people on suspicion of aggravated trespassing, while the wider rally voiced support for a “free Iran,” reflecting how Iran’s political tensions continue to resonate among diaspora communities abroad.</p><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Embassy setting: Witnesses and video placed the flag swap on a balcony of the Iranian mission near Hyde Park, a high-visibility spot for central London demonstrations.</li><li>Old emblem: The hoisted banner was described as a tricolour featuring the lion-and-sun motif, along with royal symbols associated with Iran’s pre-revolution era.</li><li>Crowd message: Organizers and participants framed the London gathering as solidarity with calls for political change in Iran, with hundreds rallying for a “free Iran”.</li><li>Protest backdrop: Reporting linked the overseas demonstration to unrest inside Iran that began on Dec. 28 and spread nationwide, underscoring the ongoing scale of dissent.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Protesters in London: Demonstrators used the pre-revolution flag and slogans like “free Iran” to signal support for political change and solidarity with protests in Iran. (<a href='https://www.timesofisrael.com/protester-replaces-islamic-republic-flag-with-shah-era-banner-at-irans-london-embassy/'>The Times of Israel</a>)</li><li>UK police: Police treated the incident as a security and access matter at a diplomatic site, arresting two people on suspicion of aggravated trespassing. (<a href='https://www.timesofisrael.com/protester-replaces-islamic-republic-flag-with-shah-era-banner-at-irans-london-embassy/'>The Times of Israel</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/protesters-put-pre-islamic-revolution-iran-flag-on-london-embassy-10616566#publisher=newsstand'>Protesters Put Pre-Islamic Revolution Iran Flag On London Embassy</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.timesofisrael.com/protester-replaces-islamic-republic-flag-with-shah-era-banner-at-irans-london-embassy/'>Protester replaces Islamic Republic flag with shah-era banner at Iran’s London embassy</a> - timesofisrael.com</li><li><a href='https://www.al-monitor.com/originals/2026/01/protester-put-pre-islamic-revolution-iran-flag-london-embassy-witnesses'>Protester put pre-Islamic revolution Iran flag on London embassy: witnesses</a> - al-monitor.com</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/protester-puts-pre-islamic-revolution-iran-flag-on-london-embassy'>Protester puts pre-Islamic revolution Iran flag on London embassy</a> - straitstimes.com</li></ul>